name: Andrew Sq Room Close to T&Shops
description:
Single private bedroom available in a 3 bedroom apartment. Large bright room with good sized closet and large windows with lots of natural light, cozy yet spacious with high ceilings.

Great location, minutes walking from the T with a 10 minute ride to downtown and 20 minutes to the airport. Close to the beach, grocery store, BMC, MIT, UMASS.
